reviewText: Everything I have ordered is so fantastic!!!  I love how GOD is using Jesse Duplantis through humor.  He is very funny!!!  Putting a humorous spin on everyday life. We NEED GOD & we Need humor!!!
Funny with a heart felt message.

I like Jesse Duplantis.  This is a great series to encourage you in your faith, as well as remind you to laugh along the way.  God has a sense of humor, so why shouldn't we?  Can't wait to watch all of it...

Brother Jesse Duplantis delivers another winning compliation of his hilarious stories.  They are real to life and very enjoyable - especially for Christians who are familiar with Jesse's ministry. IF not preaching he would fill houses as a stand-up but this humor is CLEAN and contains bits of Godly wisdom.  Very enjoyable! Wonderful for "movie night" at home or as gifts for the lonely or ill. Laughter is the best medicine and this DVD is good healthy dose for sure.
